quote_last: "I didn't know if I should have brought a bodyguard" he was saying as he strode in the door, a Master of the Universe with a leather jacket slung over his shoulder.
quote_raw:
Sunday, April 5
10:39 P.M.
"I didn't know if I should have brought a bodyguard" he was saying as he strode in the door, a Master of the Universe with a leather jacket slung over his shoulder.
title: Syndrome
author: Thomas Hoover
